    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once slightly charred, flip the <strong>patties </strong>over</p><p>Top <strong>half </strong>the patties with your <strong>sliced vegan cheese</strong> and cook, covered, for a final 2-3 min or until slightly charred and cooked through – these are your <strong>chilli smash patties</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, combine the<strong> chilli butter </strong>with your <strong>vegan mayo</strong>,<strong> half </strong>your<strong> white wine vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a<strong> </strong>pinch of <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>firesauce</strong></p>",
