    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build the burger, top the <strong>warmed brioche base </strong>with an <strong>outer lettuce leaf</strong>, 2 <strong>chilli smash patties</strong>, a generous dollop of the <strong>firesauce </strong>and a <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>brioche</strong> <strong>lid</strong> – this is your <strong>inferno chilli cheese smash patty burger</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>lettuce wedges </strong>and drizzle over the<strong> remaining white wine vinegar </strong>and a little drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>with the <strong>potato wedges </strong>and any<strong> remaining firesauce </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
